query search($filter: SearchFilter!) {
  search(filter: $filter) {
    meta {
      page
      totalPages
      totalRecords
    }
    results {
      ... on Organisation {
        id
        routingCode
        name
        type
        logo {
          sizes {
            url
            dimensions {
              width
              height
            }
          }
        }
        tenant {
          id
          name
          logo {
            sizes {
              url
              dimensions {
                width
                height
              }
            }
          }
          slug
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

=== parent.id))\n      .filter((fee): fee is (typeof fees)[number] => Boolean(fee))\n\n    // Get non-category-based fees (discounts, etc.)\n    const otherFees = fees.filter(\n      fee =>\n        !isCategoryBasedFee(fee) &&\n        fee.id !== currentlySelectedFeeId &&\n        !parentChainIds.has(fee.id || ''),\n    )\n\n    // Order: selected fee first, then parents (childparent), then other fees\n    return [selectedFee, ...parentFees, ...otherFees]\n  }, [fees, selectedCategoryBasedFeeIDs])\n\n  const registrationFeeData: RegistrationFeeData = useMemo(() => {\n    return fees\n      .filter(fee => fee.__typename === 'ParticipantFee')\n      .reduce(\n        (acc, fee) => {\n          return {\n            total: acc.total + fee.amount.net,\n            currencyCode: fee.amount.currency.code, // This will be the last fee's currency (they should all be the same)\n          }\n        },\n        { total: 0, currencyCode: '' },\n      )\n  }, [fees])\n\n  const hasRegistrationInsurance = availableInsurances.find(\n    insurance => insurance.type === 'REGISTRATION',\n  )\n\n  const selectedRegistrationInsurance = selectedInsurances.find(\n    insurance => insurance.type === 'REGISTRATION',\n  )\n\n  return (\n    <Card padding=\"m\" gap=\"l\" backgroundColor=\"blueberry100\">\n      <OrderSummaryText size=\"24\" weight=\"700\">\n        {t('pages.registrationordersummary.summary')}\n      </OrderSummaryText>\n      <Stack gap=\"m\">\n        {displayFees.map((fee, index) => (\n          <>\n            {isCategoryBasedFee(fee) ? (\n              <CategoryBasedRegistrationFee\n                key={`fee-${fee.id || index}`}\n                fee={fee}\n                currency={currency}\n              />\n            ) : (\n              <RegistrationFee\n                key={`fee-${fee.id || index}`}\n                fee={fee}\n                currency={currency}\n                products={products}\n              />\n            )}\n\n            <OrderSummaryHR\n              key={`fee-${fee.id || index}-divider`}\n              borderColor=\"blueberry400\"\n            />\n          </>\n        ))}\n        {vouchers?.map((voucher, index) => (\n          <>\n            <RegistrationVoucherItem\n              key={`voucher-${voucher.id}`}\n              voucher={voucher}\n              currency={currency}\n              onRemoveVoucher={onRemoveVoucher}\n            />\n            {index < fees.length - 1 && (\n              <OrderSummaryHR key={`voucher-${voucher.id}-divider`} />\n            )}\n          </>\n        ))}\n        {promotionalVouchers?.map((voucher, index) => (\n          <>\n            <RegistrationVoucherItem\n              key={`promotional-voucher-${voucher.id}`}\n              voucher={voucher}\n              currency={currency}\n              onRemoveVoucher={onRemoveVoucher}\n            />\n            {index < fees.length - 1 && (\n              <OrderSummaryHR\n                key={`promotional-voucher-${voucher.id}-divider`}\n              />\n            )}\n          </>\n        ))}\n        {externalVouchers?.map((externalVoucher, index) => (\n          <RegistrationExternalVoucherItem\n            key={`external-voucher-${externalVoucher.scheme.id}`}\n            externalVoucher={externalVoucher}\n            index={index}\n          />\n        ))}\n        <FeatureFlag name=\"layup-charity-on-checkout\">\n          {availableCharities.length > 0 && (\n            <AvailableCharitiesContainer>\n              <DonationsOnRegistration\n                selectedCharities={selectedCharities}\n                availableCharities={availableCharities}\n <FeatureFlag name=\"registration-insurance\">\n          {hasRegistrationInsurance && (\n            <RegistrationInsurance\n              selectedRegistrationInsurance={selectedRegistrationInsurance}\n              registrationFeeData={registrationFeeData}\n            />\n          )}\n        </FeatureFlag>\n      </Stack>\n      <Stack gap=\"s\">\n        {subtotalAmount > 0 && (\n          <>\n            <Stack\n              direction=\"row\"\n              justifyContent=\"space-between\"\n              alignItems=\"center\"\n            >\n              <OrderSummaryText weight=\"500\" size=\"12\">\n                {t('pages.registrationordersummary.subtotal')}\n              </OrderSummaryText>\n\n              <OrderSummaryText weight=\"500\">\n                {currency.format(subtotalAmount / 100)}\n              </OrderSummaryText>\n            </Stack>\n          </>\n        )}\n        {subtotalAmount && locale.isCA && (\n          <>\n            <Stack\n              direction=\"row\"\n              justifyContent=\"space-between\"\n              alignItems=\"center\"\n {currency.format(\n                  calculateTaxOnSubtotal(\n                    taxAmount,\n                    totalAmount,\n                    serviceFeeAmount,\n                    subtotalAmount,\n                    instalmentProcessingFeeAmount,\n                  ) / 100,\n                )}\n              </OrderSummaryText>\n            </Stack>\n          </>\n # TypeScript export type Profile (D:\Devkit\MyHoopsPHQ\_schemsts_to_gql\assets-1\index.b20384c6.js.map)
# --------------------------------------------------
export type Profile = {\n  __typename?: 'Profile';\n  /** Accreditations, training certifications and their completion status */\n  accreditations?: Maybe<Array<ProfileAccreditation>>;\n  address?: Maybe<Address>;\n  childSafety?: Maybe<Array<FieldSet>>;\n  childSafetyChecks?: Maybe<Array<ProfileChildSafetyCheck>>;\n  coachingAccreditation?: Maybe<CoachingAccreditation>;\n  concussionIncidents?: Maybe<Array<Incident>>;\n  countryOfBirth?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  dateOfBirth?: Maybe<Scalars['ISODate']>;\n  dependants?: Maybe<Array<Profile>>;\n  disabilities?: Maybe<Array<TenantField>>;\n  /** @deprecated use hasDisability and disabilities */\n  disability?: Maybe<TenantField>;\n  disabilityHelp?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  /**\n   * Returns a list of profiles that are possible duplicates of this one.\n   * The matching criteria is as follows:\n   *\n   * - The last name MUST be an exact match\n   * - The first name MUST be an exact match OR be an alternative name\n   * - The gender MUST be an exact match\n   * - The date of birth MUST be an exact match\n   *\n   * > Alternative names are commonly known aliases for a given name. For example,\n   * > `Catherine` can be an alias to `Cat`.\n   *\n   * This can be used in two different flows; in a registration or direct\n   * flow. Registration flows should provide the `registrationCode` argument\n   * which is used to verify whether duplicate profiles have existing registrations\n   * with the organisation for given registration.\n   *\n   * For example, if `registrationCode` `alice` is provided and is organised by\n   * organisation `bob`, then duplicate profiles must have a previous registration\n   * with organisation `bob`.\n   *\n   * Direct flows can provide a first name, last name, gender and/or a date of birth.\n   * Direct flows are used outside an registration context and the `registrationCode`\n   * should not be supplied in these circumstances. When these are supplied, these\n   * values are used to as part of the matching criteria instead.\n   *\n   * A request that mixes these arguments would result in a bad request.\n   *\n   * Use the `Query.duplicateProfiles` for direct flows.\n   */\n  duplicateProfiles?: Maybe<Array<DuplicateProfile>>;\n  email?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  emergencyContact?: Maybe<EmergencyContact>;\n  /**\n   * Used to store links to external accounts\n   * For example, it can store the link to someones Cricket ID account\n   */\n  externalAccounts: Array<ExternalAccount>;\n  firstName: Scalars['String'];\n  gender?: Maybe<TenantField>;\n  genderSelfDescribe?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  guardian1CountryOfBirth?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  guardian2CountryOfBirth?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  guardianBornOverseas?: Maybe<TenantField>;\n  guardians?: Maybe<Array<PossibleGuardian>>;\n  hasDisability?: Maybe<TenantField>;\n  homeNumber?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  id: Scalars['ID'];\n  identityVerificationRequired?: Maybe<Scalars['Boolean']>;\n  identityVerifications?: Maybe<Array<IdentityVerification>>;\n  indigenousDescent?: Maybe<TenantField>;\n  /**\n   * Resolves to the last known interacted organisations that the profile is associated with.\n   * This interaction is determined by their tenant. For example, this could reflect the\n   * organisation associated with the profile's last known registration and/or their latest\n   * club affiliation.\n   */\n  lastInteractedOrganisations?: Maybe<Array<DiscoverOrganisation>>;\n  lastName: Scalars['String'];\n  /** Endurance zone membership reward url */\n  membershipRewardUrl?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  memberships: Array<Membership>;\n  migratedEmail?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  migrationID?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  mobileNumber?: Maybe<Mobile>;\n  /**\n   * List of teams that the profile has participated in. Can be filtered by\n   * season status (e.g. to hide teams in completed seasons)\n   */\n  myTeamsList?: Maybe<MyTeamsList>;\n  nationalityVerifications: Array<NationalityVerification>;\n  otherDisability?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  /** The signed URL which points to photo to verify the identity of a person IRL. */\n  photoVerificationURL?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  preferredName?: Maybe<Scalars['String']>;\n  profilePhotoVerificationURL?: Maybe<SignedUrl>;\n  profileQuestions?: Maybe<Array<FieldSet>>;\n  registrationHistory?: Maybe<Array<RegistrationHistory>>;\n  socialTeams: Array<TeamOrigin>;\n  transferRequests: Array<TransferRequest>;\n  videoConsent?: Maybe<Scalars['Boolean']>;\n  visaClassifications: Array<VisaClassification>;\n  visible: Scalars['Boolean'];\n  wwc?: Maybe<Wwc>;\n};

export type UpcomingTeamEventTimeline = {\n  __typename?: 'UpcomingTeamEventTimeline';\n  /**\n   * Events have occurred recently (no more than 1 day ago), and events that are upcoming next\n   * week are found here. Most events will be allocated games of any status and some byes.\n   * Byes are represented as `DiscoverRound`.\n   *\n   * Bookmarked entries that would result in duplicated entries are removed. Duplication is\n   * determined by the type of event and the team. For example, if a user follows two teams\n   * that would play against one another, the game would be duplicated.\n   * Byes act differently as their identity is compounded by their round ID and the team.\n   * If the user follows multiple teams that share a bye (i.e., these teams are having byes\n   * on the same round), a record for each team will be given.\n   */\n  recentAndNextWeekEvents: Array<UpcomingTeamEvent>;\n  /**\n   * Upcoming events outside the week range specified above will reside in this type. export type ClaimProfileInput = {\n  claimProfileID: Scalars['ID'];\n  id: Scalars['ID'];\n  /**\n   * This field is used only for self initiated profile claiming, specifically\n   * for claiming profiles that should be classed as dependants under the account\n   * holder who should be the same as the authenticated profile.\n   *\n   * This should be set to true when the following intent is expressed from the user:\n   *\n   * - The authenticated user (also known as the account holder thereafter) wants to\n   * claim a profile as a new dependent.\n   * - The account holder knows the personal details of the dependent and submits them\n   * as override fields\n   *\n   * When this field is true, the `id` field of `ClaimProfileInput` should be the same\n   * as the account holder's profile ID while the `claimProfileID` should be the disjointed\n   * dependant profile ID.\n   *\n   * This field should not be provided and will be ignored if the `registrationCode`\n   * is also supplied.\n   */\n  isClaimingNewDependant?: InputMaybe<Scalars['Boolean']>;\n  method?: InputMaybe<ClaimMethod>;\n  registrationCode?: InputMaybe<Scalars['String']>;\n};

query getRegistration($code: String!, $role: SeasonRegistrationUserType, $skipTenantConfig: Boolean!) {
  registrationSettings(code: $code) {
    ... on DiscoverRegistration {
      id
      type
      registrationCode
      startDate {
        date
        time
        timezone
      }
      endDate {
        date
        time
        timezone
      }
      season {
        ... on DiscoverSeason {
          id
          name
          competition {
            id
            name
            organisation {
              ...RegistrationOrganisationDetails
            }
          }
        }
        ... on ProgramSeason {
          id
          name
          program {
            id
            name
            alias
          }
        }
      }
      organisation {
        id
        name
        email
        contactNumber
        websiteUrl
        address {
          id
          line1
          suburb
          postcode
          state
          country
        }
        logo {
          sizes {
            url
            dimensions {
              width
              height
            }
          }
        }
        contacts {
          id
          firstName
          lastName
          position
          email
          phone
        }
        shopVisible
      }
      products(role: $role) {
        ...ProductFragment
      }
      deferredFees
      deferredFeesDueDate
      instalmentEnabled
      visible
    }
    ... on DiscoverSocialTeamRegistration {
      id
      registrationCode
      startDate {
        date
        time
        timezone
      }
      endDate {
        date
        time
        timezone
      }
      season {
        id
        name
        competition {
          id
          name
          organisation {
            ...RegistrationOrganisationDetails
          }
        }
      }
      grades {
        id
        name
      }
      products {
        ...ProductFragment
      }
      visible
    }
  }
  tenantConfiguration @skip(if: $skipTenantConfig) {
    label
    stripePublicKey
    sport {
      name
    }
    ...TenantContactRolesConfiguration
    ...ExternalAccountLinking
  }
}

    }

query myTeamsLadder($teamID: ID!) {
  discoverTeam(teamID: $teamID) {
    id
    name
    season {
      id
      name
      competition {
        id
        type
      }
    }
    grade {
      id
      name
      ladderType
      ladder(filter: {teamID: $teamID}) {
        pool {
          id
          name
        }
        generatedFrom {
          id
          name
        }
        standings {
          team {
            id
            name
            season {
              id
              name
              competition {
                id
                name
              }
            }
            organisation {
              id
              name
              type
            }
          }
          played
          won
          lost
          drawn
          byes
          pointsFor
          pointsAgainst
          pointsDifference
          forfeits
          disqualifications
          adjustments
          percentage
          alternatePercentage
          competitionPoints
          pointsAverage
          noResults
          ties
          quotient
          netRunRate
          runsFor
          oversFaced
          wicketsLost
          runsAgainst
          oversBowled
          wicketsTaken
          winOutright
          winFirstInnings
          lossOutright
          lossFirstInnings
          matchRatio
          bonusPoints
          losingBonus
          tryBonus
          triesFor
          triesAgainst
          tryDifference
        }
        gameTypeValue
      }
      gameTypes {
        name
        value
        ladderFields {
          shortName
          key
          toolTip
          extendedToolTip
          type
          displayOrder
          dataType
          decimals
        }
        ladderRankingFields {
          fullName
          shortName
          key
          sortOrder
          toolTip
        }
      }
      overallLadder {
        ladderType
      }
      overallLadderFields {
        shortName
        key
        toolTip
        type
        displayOrder
        dataType
        decimals
      }
      overallLadderRankingFields {
        fullName
        shortName
        key
        sortOrder
        toolTip
      }
    }
    organisation {
      name
    }
  }
}

query myTeamsSquad($teamID: ID!, $profileID: ID) {
  discoverTeam(teamID: $teamID) {
    id
    season {
      id
      endDate
      status {
        value
      }
    }
  }
  myTeamsTeam(input: {teamID: $teamID, profileID: $profileID}) {
    id
    hasManagementAccess
    teamPlayers {
      participant {
        id
        profile {
          ...MyTeamsSquadProfileFragment
          videoConsent
        }
        gamesPlayed
        totalStatistics {
          type {
            shortName
            value
          }
          count
        }
      }
      playerNumber
      captain {
        name
        value
        shortName
      }
    }
    coach {
      id
      profile {
        ...MyTeamsSquadProfileFragment
      }
    }
    assistantCoaches {
      id
      profile {
        ...MyTeamsSquadProfileFragment
      }
    }
    teamManagers {
      id
      profile {
        ...MyTeamsSquadProfileFragment
      }
    }
    organiser {
      ...MyTeamsSquadProfileFragment
    }
    registrationCode
  }
  tenantConfiguration {
    statistics {
      seasonStatisticsMeta {
        value
        isDisplayable
        inOffenceList
        offenceListPublicVisible
        shortName
        name
      }
    }
    videoConsentEnabled
  }
}

          url

            height
            width
          }
        }
      }
      isTenantOrganisation
    }

    body
    image {
      heroImageUrl
      caption
    }
    products @include(if: $includeProducts) {
      ...PostProduct
    }
    publishedDateTime
    updatedDateTime
  }
}

    label
    statistics {
      enabled
      careerStatisticsMeta {
        value
        name
        shortName
        isDisplayable
      }
      seasonStatisticsMeta {
        value
        name
        shortName
        isDisplayable
      }
    }
  }
  publicProfileStatistics(profileID: $profileID) {
    careerStatistics {
      totalStatistics {
        count
        details {
          value
        }
        gameFormat
      }
      clubStatistics {
        id
        club {
          id
          name
        }
        statistics {
          count
          details {
            value
          }
          gameFormat
        }
      }
    }
    seasonStatistics {
      name
      player {
        hasGamePermit
      }
      statistics {
        season {
          id
          name
          competition {
            id
            name
            organisation {
              id
              name
            }
          }
        }
        role
        club {
          id
          name
        }
        totalStatistics {
          count
          details {
            value
          }
          gameFormat
        }
        teamStatistics {
          team {
            ... on DiscoverTeam {
              id
              name
            }
          }
          totalStatistics {
            count
            details {
              value
            }
            gameFormat
          }
          gradeStatistics {
            grade {
              id
              name
            }
            totalStatistics {
              count
              details {
                value
              }
              gameFormat
            }
            gameStatistics {
              game {
                id
                round {
                  name
                }
                home {
                  ... on DiscoverTeam {
                    id
                    name
                  }
                }
                away {
                  ... on DiscoverTeam {
                    id
                    name
                  }
                }
                date
                allocation {
                  court {
                    abbreviatedName
                    venue {
                      name
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
              statistics {
                count
                details {
                  value
                }
                gameFormat
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
  publicProfile(profileID: $profileID) {
    id
    firstName
    lastName
  }
}

query registrationOverview($code: String!) {
  registrationSettings(code: $code) {
    ... on DiscoverRegistration {
      id
      type
      season {
        ... on DiscoverSeason {
          id
          name
          startDate
          endDate
          competition {
            id
            name
            organisation {
              id
              name
            }
          }
          ageRestrictionRange {
            dobFromDate
            dobToDate
          }
          ageGroups {
            ageGroup {
              name
              value
            }
            equalToOrOlderThan {
              years
              months
              days
            }
            youngerThan {
              years
              months
              days
            }
            minDOB
            maxDOB
          }
        }
        ... on ProgramSeason {
          id
          name
          startDate
          endDate
          program {
            id
            name
            alias
          }
        }
      }
      registrationUserTypes {
        name
        displayName
        value
      }
      organisation {
        id
        name
      }
      pricingInfo
      additionalInfo
      registrationAgeRestriction {
        asAtDate
        range {
          min
          max
        }
      }
      groups {
        ...GroupLabel
      }
      ageGroupRestrictions {
        ageGroup {
          value
        }
        registrationInfo
      }
      daySessions {
        day
        startTime
        endTime
      }
      sessionCount
      gender
      playingSurface {
        id
        name
        venue {
          id
          name
        }
      }
    }
    ... on DiscoverSocialTeamRegistration {
      id
      season {
        ... on DiscoverSeason {
          id
          name
          startDate
          endDate
          competition {
            id
            name
            organisation {
              id
              name
            }
          }
        }
      }
      pricingInfo
      additionalInfo
    }
  }
}

        selfSubmit

          name
          value
        }
      }
      disabilities {
        name
        value
      }
    }
    discloseOptions {
      name
      value
    }
    sport {
      name
    }
    videoConsentEnabled
  }
  configuration {
    supportedCountries {
      name
      alpha2Code
      mobileCountryCode
    }
  }
  discoverSeasonRegistration(registrationID: $registrationId) {
    id
    type
    questions {
      id
      question
    }
    customFields(role: $role) {
      ...TextCustomFieldDetails
      ...RecursiveDropdownCustomFieldsDetails
    }
    groups {
      ...GroupLabel
      userTypesMeta {
        name
        value
        registrationLimit {
          limitReached
        }
        fee {
          net
        }
      }
    }
    fieldEntries(profileID: $profileID) {
      childSafety {
        ...FieldSetFragment
      }
      profileQuestions {
        ...FieldSetFragment
      }
    }
    season {
      ... on DiscoverSeason {
        id
        startDate
      }
      ... on ProgramSeason {
        id
        startDate
      }
    }
  }
}

    id
    profile {

      lastName

        value
      }

      dateOfBirth
      mobileNumber {
        countryAlphaCode
        countryCode {
          value
        }
        number
        displayNumber
      }
      preferredName
      countryOfBirth
      homeNumber
      indigenousDescent {
        value
      }
      address {
        id
        line1
        suburb
        postcode
        state
        country
      }
      emergencyContact {
        id
        firstName
        lastName
        email
        mobileNumber {
          countryAlphaCode
          countryCode {
            value
          }
          displayNumber
          number
        }
        relation
      }
      guardians {
        ... on Profile {
          id
          firstName
          lastName
          email

      }

    }

      ladder(filter: {teamID: $teamID}) {
        pool {
          id

  }

      }

      name
      value
    }

      name
    }
  }
  discoverOrganisation(code: $organisationCode) {
    ...OrganisationDetails
  }
}
